            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Programme wiederholen dieselben Codezeilen immer wieder, um alle möglichen Dinge zu erstellen, wie die wiederholten Elemente in der App unten.</p><webview version=\"2\" visible-if=\"always\" content=\"&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;&#xA;&lt;html&gt;&#xA;  &lt;head&gt;&#xA;    &lt;title&gt;Pick your sport&lt;/title&gt;&#xA;    &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css&quot; /&gt;&#xA;    &lt;style&gt;&#xA;      body {&#xA;        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&#xA;        background: #f0f2f5;&#xA;        display: flex;&#xA;        flex-direction: column;&#xA;        align-items: center;&#xA;        margin: 0;&#xA;      }&#xA;&#xA;      h1 {&#xA;        background-color: #004d99;&#xA;        color: white;&#xA;        padding: 20px;&#xA;        border-radius: 10px;&#xA;        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);&#xA;      }&#xA;&#xA;      .icon-list {&#xA;        background: white;&#xA;        list-style-type: none;&#xA;        padding: 20px;&#xA;        border-radius: 10px;&#xA;        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);&#xA;        width: 300px;&#xA;      }&#xA;&#xA;      .icon-list li {&#xA;        display: flex;&#xA;        align-items: center;&#xA;        margin: 10px 0;&#xA;        font-size: 22px;&#xA;        font-weight: bold;&#xA;        background-color: #e0f7fa;&#xA;        padding: 10px;&#xA;        border-radius: 5px;&#xA;        transition: background-color 0.3s;&#xA;      }&#xA;&#xA;      .icon-list li:hover {&#xA;        background-color: #b2ebf2;&#xA;      }&#xA;&#xA;      .icon-list li i {&#xA;        margin-right: 15px;&#xA;        color: #004d99;&#xA;        font-size: 30px;&#xA;      }&#xA;    &lt;/style&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/head&gt;&#xA;  &lt;body&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h1&gt;Sports&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;    &lt;ul class=&quot;icon-list&quot;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;li&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-football-ball&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Football&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;li&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-basketball-ball&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Basketball&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;li&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-baseball-ball&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Baseball&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;li&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-volleyball-ball&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Volleyball&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;script src=&quot;script.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/body&gt;&#xA;&lt;/html&gt;\" /></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Intro 2",
            "id": 78314,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Eine Möglichkeit, Codezeilen zu wiederholen, besteht darin, sie immer wieder zu schreiben, aber das dauert wirklich lange, wenn wir größere Programme erstellen wollen.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"82\" endIndex=\"83\" /><option startIndex=\"83\" endIndex=\"92\" /><option startIndex=\"92\" endIndex=\"93\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>\"</code>, gefolgt von <code>and again</code> und schließlich <code>\"</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Intro 3",
            "id": 78313,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Um größere Programme und Websites zu erstellen, wiederholen wir Codezeilen mit einer <strong>while-Schleife</strong>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\": \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"5\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"if\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>while</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "While loop",
            "id": 78310,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Die Verwendung einer while-Schleife, um Codezeilen zu wiederholen, beginnt mit dem <code>while</code>-Schlüsselwort.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"5\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Gib <code>while</code> ein.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "While loop",
            "id": 78309,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Eine while-Schleife wiederholt ihren Codeblock, solange ihre Bedingung <code>True</code> ist. Wir codieren eine <code>True</code>-Bedingung mit <code>True</code> gefolgt von einem Doppelpunkt <code>:</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"11\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Gib <code>True:</code> ein.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "While loop",
            "id": 78308,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Der Code, den die <code>while</code>-Schleife wiederholt, kommt nach dem <code>:</code>, innerhalb des eingerückten Codeblocks. Wie die <code>print()</code>-Anweisung hier.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\": \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"33\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>print(\"and again\")</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "While loop",
            "id": 78312,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Wenn die Bedingung einer <code>while</code>-Schleife für immer <code>True</code> bleibt, nennen wir das eine <strong>Endlosschleife</strong>, da sie unendlich schleifen wird, wie hier mit <code>print()</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\": \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"20\" /><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"21\" /><option startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"32\" /><option startIndex=\"32\" endIndex=\"33\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>print</code>, gefolgt von <code>(</code> und schließlich <code>\"and again\"</code>, <code>)</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
